Privacy Policy for Status Saver

At Status Saver, the privacy of our users is extremely important to us. This privacy policy outlines the types of information that we may collect from users of our application, as well as how we use, store, and protect that information.

Information Collection and Use

Status Saver does not collect any personal information or data from our users. We do not collect any data related to your browsing history, location, or any other personal information.

Advertising

To generate revenue, our application includes third-party ads through Google Play Console. These ads may collect anonymous data related to your browsing history or device to serve personalized ads. However, we do not have access to this data.

Cookies

Status Saver does not use cookies to collect any user data.

Third-party Links

Our application may contain links to third-party websites or applications. Please be aware that we are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party sites. We encourage our users to read the privacy policies of any third-party site they visit.

Security

We take all necessary measures to ensure the security of our application and protect the privacy of our users. We use industry-standard security protocols to prevent unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure of any user data that may be collected.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to make changes to this privacy policy at any time. Any changes made will be reflected in an updated privacy policy on our website.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy policy, please contact us at gabrieloranekwu@gmail.com.

By using Status Saver, you agree to the terms of this privacy policy.



